<!doctype html>
<html><head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>H38-T007 Cleanup Rescue Pack</title><style>@page{margin:.6in}body{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.45;color:#111827;max-width:8.1in;margin:0 auto;background:#fff}h1{background:#1f2937;color:#fff;padding:16px 18px;border-radius:10px;font-size:22pt;margin:0 0 14px}h2{color:#0f172a;border-bottom:2px solid #cbd5e1;padding-bottom:4px;margin:18px 0 8px;font-size:15pt}p{margin:8px 0 12px}ul{margin:8px 0 14px 24px}li{margin:4px 0}table{border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;table-layout:fixed;margin:10px 0 16px}th,td{border:1px solid #b7c3d0;padding:8px 9px;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word}th{background:#dbeafe;color:#0f172a;text-align:left}.meta{background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #dbe3ec;border-radius:10px;padding:10px 12px}.visual{text-align:center;margin:12px 0 16px}.visual img{width:100%;max-width:7.15in;height:auto;border:1px solid #cbd5e1;border-radius:10px}.note{background:#f8fafc;border-left:6px solid #64748b;padding:10px 12px;margin:12px 0 16px;border-radius:6px}</style></head><body><h1>Highway 38 Solutions - Cleanup Rescue Pack</h1><p class="meta"><b>Sample ID:</b> H38-T007<br><b>Scenario:</b> Folder dump to cleanup index</p><div class="visual"><img src="../assets/sample-cleanup-proof.svg" alt="Cleanup rescue visual"></div><h2>Customer input</h2><ul><li>Receipts, screenshots, project photos, notes, links, and mixed folder names.</li><li>Problem: owner cannot find proof, cost notes, or next actions.</li><li>Goal: separate reference, proof, receipts, action items, and archive.</li></ul><h2>Folder map</h2><table><colgroup><col style="width:28%"><col style="width:42%"><col style="width:30%"></colgroup><tr><th>Folder</th><th>What goes there</th><th>Rule</th></tr><tr><td>01 Receipts</td><td>Purchases, order confirmations, paid invoices.</td><td>Use date_vendor_amount.</td></tr><tr><td>02 Proof Photos</td><td>Before, during, after, damage, progress.</td><td>Keep original photos.</td></tr><tr><td>03 Reference</td><td>Links, product ideas, sketches, notes.</td><td>Not proof, not action.</td></tr><tr><td>04 Action Needed</td><td>Anything requiring reply, purchase, or decision.</td><td>Every item needs owner action.</td></tr><tr><td>99 Archive</td><td>Old or inactive files.</td><td>Do not delete unless confirmed.</td></tr></table><h2>Customer-ready summary</h2><div class="note">Your files are not useless; they are mixed. The first win is to sort proof from action so the next reply, purchase, or decision is visible.</div></body></html>